<task id="task_f4z_t4l_jp">
    <title>Editing tags in the structure menu</title>
    <shortdesc>You can edit any of the tags that pre-exist in the template or that you have added to
        the document. This also allows you to add contextual information through
        attributes.</shortdesc>
